      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a reliable source for parts? This vehicle is ready for someone with a mechanical touch to give it some TLC! While it currently needs significant repairs and is in poor condition, it offers a fantastic opportunity for a DIY enthusiast to bring it back to life or utilize its components. Grab this diamond in the rough at a great price!",
